Subject: [PATCH 11/22] feat(node-governance): add export/import service
 methods for categories

Add exportCategories() and importCategories() methods to NodeGovernanceService
for exporting and importing category configurations with node assignments.

- Export creates JSON with version, timestamp, and categories with nodes
- Import uses upsert: updates existing categories by slug, creates new ones
- Node assignments are synced (removed if not in import, added if new)
